   The only T shirt I wear now

   All other t-shirts are now just a distant, clammy memory. I wore my old
   Uniqlo tee the other day, within an hour or two the cotton felt itchy
   and clammy and coarse. Why did it feel so bad, you say?
   Because ever since I got an action merino, I wear nothing but. They are
   the softest, most flattering tops I have worn in my life. They can
   survive hot sweaty jungles, ice cold walks in winter and long haul
   flights - all coming out of it smelling like you just washed them.
   Seriously. All the comments above and below cannot lie and neither does
   this review. Try one and you'll see why I threw all the others out.
   Cons: they are a little delicate. Perhaps as the brand grows and
   adapts, they will tweak the material to be a bit stronger. You can do
   it Seagale!

